Burn these songs to a disc.. did you write that right.. because the answer is No!.. i own the original discs Yes.. I ripped 99% with Dbpoweramp the first few rips were 3.98r and the rest 3.99a all set at the same setting of vbrv0.. the 1% more or less were done with EAC.. and some songs didn rip with either so they were left out altogether.. it's the same i'm going to do with the Flac i've got.. i will use Dbpoweramp again... :).. the only time i use EAC is when ripping a new CD release because i actually make the Flac first for myself and then change the profile!

no i named it the ultimate collection.. go read the desript... in Pt.1... by me naming it the ultimate collection i sought of raised the bar a bit a challenge to myself.. so it could never end! thus why it's in parts so when i do run out of 80's songs and then i can still gather some more as i come across them and post the next Pt.. so on and on.... i couldn't do 1 big collection because i would of left heaps out.. :)
